# ASU Desi Hub

Apartment directory + sublease board built for Indian international students at Arizona State University.

## What this is
1. **Apartment directory** — real resident photos, honest management reviews, quick facts for every major complex near ASU
2. **Sublease board** — structured listings tied to apartments in the directory, filterable by what actually matters (gender, diet, dates, rent)
3. **Add-ons** (later) — move-out sales, roommate requests, static guides for transit/food/attractions

## Tech
Next.js 16, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind v4, Supabase (Postgres + Storage), MDX, Vercel.

## Inspiration
https://budgetsf.vercel.app — same clean static-guide energy, different audience and scope.

## Status
Pre-launch. Building MVP: apartment directory with 10 seeded complexes + working sublease board.